introduce: It is an open source implementation of Quantum Wormhole, which generates a unique pattern based on your name and birthday.
security-description: All of your personal data is processed locally, you can check our implementation on GitHub.
is-nft-p1: No, it isn't. But you can purchase it if you want.
is-nft-p2: Send any amount of ethereum to the following wallet, you will have the right to use Quantum Wormhole for all legal purpose, including but not limited to commercial use.
